mes New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">好巴食</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">南溪豆腐干产品，深受市场和消费者喜爱，旗下各系列产品生产工艺科学先进、产品品质优良且附加值不断攀升、市场前景广阔。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　徽记休闲食品加盟费用根本比较少，加盟商只需要投入一点点资金就可以了，而且越是投资小风险就会越小，并且可以马上见到丰厚的利润，加盟商完全可以放心加盟。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　徽记在新的历史时期确立了以人为本、科学管理、依法管理的思想。积极从建立现代管理决策体系、完善管理组织、制度流程标准和有效激效考核几方面入手，以期形成企业核心运营能力。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　目前公司的信息化、制度化、规范化管理步入正轨，公司搭建起辐射全国的市场营销网络、服务支持网络和人才培育网络，建立起雄厚的资本支持、有力的品牌支持和高效的通路支持。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　一、投资咨询</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　通过网络等方式认识和初步了解徽记食品加盟相关信息。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　二、意向沟通或实地考察</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　申请人到公司实地考察，参观加盟店；考察并对项目相关合作细节资料进行索要，全面了解下加盟的细节问题；</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　三、加盟申请审核</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　通过网站递交申请表或直接电话联系传真至公司总部加盟管理中心审核；总部审核</font> <font face=\"宋体\">总部都会对加盟方进行一个考察，看加盟方是否有正经营项目的能力；</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　四、签订合同</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　签署加盟合同，确立合作关系。合作者缴交保证金，授予特许经销牌证</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　五、店铺设计装修</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　客户在店面装修验收合格后，需按公司要求进行渠道空间认证。待审核通过后，由市场部签发</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">授权书</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　装修布置，总部可提供规划和装修设计方案，可向总部制定和采购设备、物料并可同步进行其他开业筹备工作；</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　六、开业前准备</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　加盟商备货</font>,<font face=\"宋体\">装修验收</font><font face=\"Calibri\">,</font><font face=\"宋体\">员工培训</font><font face=\"Calibri\">,</font><font face=\"宋体\">开业策划</font><font face=\"Calibri\">,</font><font face=\"宋体\">货品物料入店</font><font face=\"Calibri\">;</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　七、正式营业和后续服务</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　新店开业。落实总部各项宣传与促销措施，规范管理、管理与服务，经常和总部沟通经营情况并提出意见和建议。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　徽记在新的历史时期确立了以人为本、科学管理、依法管理的思想。积极从建立现代管理决策体系、完善管理组织、制度流程标准和有效激效考核几方面入手，以期形成企业核心运营能力。目前公司的信息化、制度化、规范化管理步入正轨，公司搭建起辐射全国的市场营销网络、服务支持网络和人才培育网络，建立起雄厚的资本支持、有力的品牌支持和高效的通路支持。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　徽记加盟的硬件要求：</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font>1<font face=\"宋体\">、能够满足总部要求的运营经济实力，自有资料在</font><font face=\"Calibri\">16</font><font face=\"宋体\">万元以上，流动资金</font><font face=\"Calibri\">2-6.5</font><font face=\"宋体\">万元。包括：房租费、装修费、设备费、物品费、加盟的加盟费和保证金及管理费等在内。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font>2<font face=\"宋体\">、所经营店门的面积</font><font face=\"Calibri\">15</font><font face=\"宋体\">平方米以上的当街店铺；门面门宽</font><font face=\"Calibri\">3</font><font face=\"宋体\">米以上，高</font><font face=\"Calibri\">3.2</font><font face=\"宋体\">米以上，门头广告招牌不少于</font><font face=\"Calibri\">3</font><font face=\"宋体\">米的宽度，门面承租期至少</font><font face=\"Calibri\">2</font><font face=\"宋体\">年以上。门面尺寸不标准的需通过公司核准放可加盟。外观造型与区域景致谐调：在设计商店外观的造型时，除了考虑建筑本身结构比例的协调性之外，还要注意使商店的外观造型与所处的区域的自然景致相协调。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font>3<font face=\"宋体\">、装修设计：加盟方提供经营场地平面图，公司负责设计装修方案及效果图。在公司的指导下，按公司统一的设计方案进行选材、装潢。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font>4<font face=\"宋体\">、加盟店整个系统的专用设备配备必须按公司统一要求配备齐全方可正常运营。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '', '');
INSERT INTO `addonarticles` VALUES ('627', '3', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　兰州正林农垦食品有限公司由台商林垦先生投资创建于</font>1991<font face=\"宋体\">年，座落在美丽的黄河之滨</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">—</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">兰州，占地</font>70<font face=\"宋体\">余亩，投资总额</font><font face=\"Calibri\">750</font><font face=\"宋体\">万美元，总资产近</font><font face=\"Calibri\">3</font><font face=\"宋体\">亿人民币。公司拥有员工</font><font face=\"Calibri\">2000</font><font face=\"宋体\">余人，将</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">有中国人的地方就有正林食品</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">作为奋斗目标，在全国各省市设立了</font>30<font face=\"宋体\">余家销售分公司。正林以</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">品质、创新、速度、服务</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">为宗旨，不断创新产品，服务于广大消费者。目前已建成黑瓜籽、白瓜籽、葵花籽、开心果、脆枣、蛋卷等产品</font>20<font face=\"宋体\">余条全不锈钢密封式自动化生产线，日生产能力超过</font><font face=\"Calibri\">200</font><font face=\"宋体\">吨。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '', '', '', '', '正林食品', '1991年', '甘肃', '200家', '5-10万', '全国', '炒货食品', '自由创业', '12415', '4156', '9874', '兰州正林农垦食品有限公司', '兰州', '否', '2017-03-20 10:04:54', '2017-03-20 10:04:54', '/images/thread/2017/03/20/967270de59e26bac2b126ddc61757834.jpg,/images/thread/2017/03/20/964a3493c62de16dd955cf9ec04644fd.jpg,/images/thread/2017/03/20/c99934c1c18bdf2ba9564d9543d2ebc7.jpg,/images/thread/2017/03/20/1495c2dfdc6a5deea325f61d45e93bba.jpg,/images/thread/2017/03/20/4a591990769a9a0103f8145f89349fb3.jpg,', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　正林公司作为一家专业生产炒货的企业，以质量为本，以消费者为本，一贯坚持做良心食品，做优质安全的食品；公司在生产加工过程中严格按照食品安全法、食品企业通用卫生规范、食品添加剂使用标准等相关食品法律、法规的要求进行，不超范围、超标添加食品添加剂，生产安全优质的产品。公司生产车间为现代化的全自动不锈钢流水生产线，设备先进，工艺先进，经过严格培训的员工，认真执着的管理人员</font>……这点点滴滴造就了正林产品，铸就了正林品牌。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　品牌优势</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　兰州正林农垦食品有限公司成立于</font>1991<font face=\"宋体\">年，主要以生产、销售</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">正林</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">品牌的各种炒货坚果类产品为主，是目前大型的一家综合炒货类生产企业，拥有先进的生产设备、强大的产品设计和开发团队。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　独特的工艺</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　选料：</font>3<font face=\"宋体\">次机器来回筛选，挑选出个头均匀，颗粒饱满的瓜子。 配料：多种配料，新配方，新工艺，口感纯正，好吃易磕。 烘烤：低温烘烤，力求保留纯正味道。 入口：简单易磕，口感好，风味独特，新配方，新工艺。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: