p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　公司对经销商进行培训和指导后方可开业。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　开业前的支持：授予各级加盟商新行家商标使用权，颁发授权铜牌及证书。协助加盟商选址，提供选址标准，并就加盟店所选店址进行评估。参与加盟店的装修设计、指导、验收、保障全国新行家连锁店</font>VI<font face=\"宋体\">系统的统一。指派培训专员到当地免费对加盟店员工进行全面的专业知识和经营管理培训。提供整套业务系统：即标准化和规范化的报表和经营管理手册。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　开业时的支持：提供首批进货及经营用品配置指导性意见。指派营运专员到当地对店面开业布置及产品陈列进行指导。免费提供开业促销活动方案及开业宣传单。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　现场专业指导支持：指导加盟商进行多种形式店外营销拓展。提供专业、快捷、安全的物流配送。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　开正林食品炒货店利润怎么样？</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　现如今的炒货市场发展非常的好，而正林食品炒货店绝对堪称其中的经典。正林食品炒货店加盟其有着独有的产品特色和口感优势，所以受到广大食客们的热捧，加盟优势明显，经营正林炒货店的话，经营的好，那么盈利是一定不会少的。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '', '');
INSERT INTO `addonarticles` VALUES ('628', '3', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　浙江大好大食品有限公司是一家集团化运作，集科研、工业、贸易为一体的民营股份制食品加工企业。总部位于温州，创办于</font>2000<font face=\"宋体\">年</font><font face=\"Calibri\">10</font><font face=\"宋体\">月，注册资金</font><font face=\"Calibri\">10500</font><font face=\"宋体\">万元。现拥有</font><font face=\"Calibri\">4</font><font face=\"宋体\">个控股子公司，总占地</font><font face=\"Calibri\">300</font><font face=\"宋体\">余亩，建筑面积达</font><font face=\"Calibri\">25</font><font face=\"宋体\">万平方米。现有员工</font><font face=\"Calibri\">1500</font><font face=\"宋体\">余人；建有</font><font face=\"Calibri\">4</font><font face=\"宋体\">个销售分公司，</font><font face=\"Calibri\">60</font><font face=\"宋体\">余处办事处，</font><font face=\"Calibri\">2000</font><font face=\"宋体\">余处经销；建立了</font><font face=\"Calibri\">31</font><font face=\"宋体\">万亩原料生产基地，辐射带动了</font><font face=\"Calibri\">4</font><font face=\"宋体\">万多农户增加收入，解决了</font><font face=\"Calibri\">1000</font><font face=\"宋体\">余人的再就业。公司为中国休闲食品行业产销的大型企业之一。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '', '', '', '', '大好大食品', '2000年', '浙江', '300家', '5-10万', '全国', '坚果炒货', '自由创业', '15421', '3254', '8412', '8412', '浙江', '否', '2017-03-20 10:07:06', '2017-03-20 10:07:06', '/images/thread/2017/03/20/ba7c245ff77cff494965cec27f4d59c3.jpg,/images/thread/2017/03/20/4b9dd0cb099d445cff54052ed21937aa.jpg,/images/thread/2017/03/20/9b5cba4020dd269c0f95fdc4c6001ee7.jpg,/images/thread/2017/03/20/399c91661ea96501244501f79d401f67.jpg,/images/thread/2017/03/20/0021348ccaba711c62dd688df578372b.jpg,', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　大好大食品加盟，炒货食品在消费者的心目中一直有着很高的地位，美味的炒货零食平时悠闲娱乐最好的选择</font>.<font face=\"宋体\">在食品界极具口碑，每一个吃过的人都忍不住的夸赞呢</font><font face=\"Calibri\">!</font><font face=\"宋体\">在我们的生活中，食品是不可缺少的，而凭借其美味占据了极大的消费市场</font><font face=\"Calibri\">.</font><font face=\"宋体\">选择加盟，好吃不贵，种类丰富多样，而且大好大食品有着不断的翻新制作出新产品，大好大 炒货店经营的好，那么盈利一定不会少。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font>1<font face=\"宋体\">、确保经销商相应区域内的独家垄断性经营权益。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font>2<font face=\"宋体\">、实施经营管理支持，根据经销商销售情况派人员驻地指导。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font>3<font face=\"宋体\">、严格控制价格的波动，并给予相应的政策，充分保证经销产品丰厚的利润空间和市场经营高额回报。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font>4<font face=\"宋体\">、提供合理的退换货保障制度，保证经销商合作零风险。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"M