-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">用良心打造品牌，用诚信铸就辉煌</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">是香满盈人的永恒追求和立业之本；是香满盈全体员工奉献给世人的一份诚挚的爱和火热的情。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　香满盈炒货坊新推出的香满盈炒货坊炒货，采用独特配方，结合现代工艺精心炒制出的各种干果迎合现代人的新消费求。香满盈炒货坊市场前景广阔，品种也随之推陈出新，从传统的南瓜子、葵花子、西瓜子占主导地位，到松子、核桃、板栗、花生等各种干果的大量采用，许多含有丰富营养的干果都进入了炒货的行列</font>;<font face=\"宋体\">制作方法从纯炒制到摇、裹、搓、蹦、煎、炸不断变化</font><font face=\"Calibri\">;</font><font face=\"宋体\">花色从不加配料的纯炒制到椒盐味、五香味、奶油味、水果味等不断创新……炒货将以前所未有的新产品、新姿态出现在人们的生活中。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font