ce=\"宋体\">厚生记休闲食品</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">品牌效应损害消费者利益。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font>5<font face=\"宋体\">、愿意接受厚生记休闲食品招商公司的统一管理。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　</font>6<font face=\"宋体\">、拥有固定的经营店面，厚生记休闲食品加盟店面符合公司加盟要求。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　开厚生记加盟店盈利如何？</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　开个厚生记加盟店是投资创业的好项目，因为，当下人们的生活水平越来越高，自然对于生活质量的要求也有了显著的提高。尤其是饮食方面，不仅在主食方面特别注重，对于三餐之外的零食更是需求度越来越高。由于现在的零食已经不同于以往的零食只有单一的品种和口味，不仅种类丰富而且口感特别好，每种产品的口味也不尽相同。因此消费者对于零食的依赖性越来越高，所以说，开个厚生记加盟店将会为投资者带来非常大的利润。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n                                                                    ', '', '');
INSERT INTO `addonarticles` VALUES ('673', '3', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　江苏阿里山食品有限公司，坚果炒货十大品牌，创建于</font>1984<font face=\"宋体\">年，江苏省著名商标，专业从事西瓜子、小胡桃、开心果等手剥炒货坚果的研发和生产的企业。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">　　江苏阿里山食品有限公司位于江南鱼米之乡</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">——</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">常熟市，毗邻上海、苏州、无锡、南通。公司创建于</font>1984<font face=\"宋体\">年，经过近</font><font face=\"Calibri\">30</font><font face=\"宋体\">多年的艰苦创业，目前资产总额超二亿元，员工</font><font face=\"Calibri\">800</font><font face=\"宋体\">余人，占地</font><font face=\"Calibri\">8</font><font face=\"宋体\">万平方米。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">阿里山</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">牌食品从单一葵花子已发展到</font>50<font face=\"宋体\">多个品种，是全国规模较大的农产品深加工基地，是江苏省农业产业化龙头企业。</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">阿里山</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">坚果炒货食品连续十多年被评为江苏省名牌产品、江苏省著名商标，</font>2009<font face=\"宋体\">年荣获</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><font 